Scope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n109194.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νέφους ὑποστάσεις</foreign> cloud-<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cumuli,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:1:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.38</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n109194.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a kind of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">jelly</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">thick soup,</tr_> in pl., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0541.tlg001:462:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Men.\">Men.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">462.10</biblScope> </bibl> (cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:6:60\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.60</biblScope> </bibl>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg001:4:8:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orib.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.8.1</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n109194.8\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph. of time, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">duration,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἡ στιγμιαία τῶν καιρῶν ὑ.</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.187</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μνήσθητι τίς μου ἡ ὑ.</foreign> remember how short my <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">time</tr_> is, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg027:88(89).48\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ LXX\">LXX</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"ti